      "message": "did you know that Convey can have sub-conveys?\n\nConvey(....., func() {\n  // initialization, e.g. create routes, install handlers, etc\n\n  Convey(........, func() {\n     // the test\n  })\n  Convey(........, func() {\n     // the test 2\n  })\n})\n\nthis is not limited to 2 levels\n\nsee how Convey is used in this repo\n\n--\n\nand then these helper functions will do only the call, without initialization",
